358class NecroticPlagueTargetCheck : public std::unary_function<Unit*, bool>
359{
360 public:
361 NecroticPlagueTargetCheck(Unit const* obj, uint32 notAura1 = 0, uint32 notAura2 = 0)
362 : _sourceObj(obj), _notAura1(notAura1), _notAura2(notAura2)
363 {
364 }
365
366 bool operator()(Unit* unit) const
367 {
368 if (!unit || unit == _sourceObj || !unit->isTargetableForAttack() || unit->GetTypeId() != TYPEID_PLAYER || unit->HasAura(SPELL_PLAGUE_AVOIDANCE))
369 return false;
370 if ((_notAura1 && unit->HasAura(_notAura1)) || (_notAura2 && unit->HasAura(_notAura2)))
371 return false;
372 return true;
373 }
374
375 private:
376 Unit const* _sourceObj;
377 uint32 _notAura1;
378 uint32 _notAura2;
379};
380
381class HeightDifferenceCheck
382{
383 public:
384 HeightDifferenceCheck(GameObject* go, float diff, bool reverse)
385 : _baseObject(go), _difference(diff), _reverse(reverse)
386 {
387 }
388
389 bool operator()(WorldObject* unit) const
390 {
391 return (unit->GetPositionZ() - _baseObject->GetPositionZ() > _difference) != _reverse;
392 }
393
394 private:
395 GameObject* _baseObject;
396 float _difference;
397 bool _reverse;
398};
399
400class FrozenThroneResetWorker
401{
402 public:
403 FrozenThroneResetWorker() { }
404
405 bool operator()(GameObject* go)
406 {
407 switch (go->GetEntry())
408 {
409 case GO_ARTHAS_PLATFORM:
410 go->SetDestructibleState(GO_DESTRUCTIBLE_REBUILDING);
411 break;
412 case GO_DOODAD_ICECROWN_THRONEFROSTYWIND01:
413 go->SetGoState(GO_STATE_ACTIVE);
414 break;
415 case GO_DOODAD_ICECROWN_THRONEFROSTYEDGE01:
416 go->SetGoState(GO_STATE_READY);
417 break;
418 case GO_DOODAD_ICESHARD_STANDING02:
419 case GO_DOODAD_ICESHARD_STANDING01:
420 case GO_DOODAD_ICESHARD_STANDING03:
421 case GO_DOODAD_ICESHARD_STANDING04:
422 go->ResetDoorOrButton();
423 break;
424 default:
425 break;
426 }
427
428 return false;
429 }
430};

432class StartMovementEvent : public BasicEvent
433{
434 public:
435 StartMovementEvent(Creature* summoner, Creature* owner)
436 : _summonerGuid(summoner->GetGUID()), _owner(owner)
437 {
438 }
439
440 bool Execute(uint64 /*time*/, uint32 /*diff*/)
441 {
442 _owner->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
443 if (Creature* _summoner = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*_owner, _summonerGuid))
444 if (Unit* target = _summoner->AI()->SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 0, NonTankTargetSelector(_summoner)))
445 _owner->AI()->AttackStart(target);
446 return true;
447 }
448
449 private:
450 ObjectGuid _summonerGuid;
451 Creature* _owner;
452};

474class TriggerWickedSpirit : public BasicEvent
475{
476 public:
477 explicit TriggerWickedSpirit(Creature* owner)
478 : _owner(owner), _counter(13)
479 {
480 }
481
482 bool Execute(uint64 /*time*/, uint32 /*diff*/)
483 {
484 _owner->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_TRIGGER_VILE_SPIRIT_HEROIC, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 1, NULL, true);
485
486 if (--_counter)
487 {
488 _owner->m_Events.AddEvent(this, _owner->m_Events.CalculateTime(3000));
489 return false;
490 }
491
492 return true;
493 }
494
495 private:
496 Creature* _owner;
497 uint32 _counter;
498};

500class boss_the_lich_king : public CreatureScript
501{
502 public:
503 boss_the_lich_king() : CreatureScript("boss_the_lich_king") { }
504
505 struct boss_the_lich_kingAI : public BossAI
506 {
507 boss_the_lich_kingAI(Creature* creature) : BossAI(creature, DATA_THE_LICH_KING)
508 {
509 Initialize();
510 }
511
512 void Initialize()
513 {
514 _necroticPlagueStack = 0;
515 _vileSpiritExplosions = 0;
516 }
517
518 void InitializeAI() override
519 {
520 SetupEncounter();
521 }
522
523 void JustRespawned() override
524 {
525 SetupEncounter();
526 }
527
528 void SetupEncounter()
529 {
530 _Reset();
531 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
532 events.SetPhase(PHASE_INTRO);
533 Initialize();
534 SetEquipmentSlots(true);
535
536 // Reset The Frozen Throne gameobjects
537 FrozenThroneResetWorker reset;
538 Trinity::GameObjectWorker<FrozenThroneResetWorker> worker(me, reset);
539 me->VisitNearbyGridObject(333.0f, worker);
540
541 // Reset any light override
542 me->GetMap()->SetZoneOverrideLight(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, 0, 5000);
543
544 me->SummonCreature(NPC_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING_LK, TirionSpawn, TEMPSUMMON_MANUAL_DESPAWN);
545 }
546
547 void JustDied(Unit* /*killer*/) override
548 {
549 _JustDied();
550 DoCastAOE(SPELL_PLAY_MOVIE, false);
551 me->SetDisableGravity(false);
552 me->RemoveByteFlag(UNIT_FIELD_BYTES_1, 3, UNIT_BYTE1_FLAG_ALWAYS_STAND | UNIT_BYTE1_FLAG_HOVER);
553 me->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFall();
554 if (Creature* frostmourne = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_FROSTMOURNE_TRIGGER, 50.0f))
555 frostmourne->DespawnOrUnsummon();
556 }
557
558 void EnterCombat(Unit* target) override
559 {
560 if (!instance->CheckRequiredBosses(DATA_THE_LICH_KING, target->ToPlayer()))
561 {
562 EnterEvadeMode(EVADE_REASON_OTHER);
563 instance->DoCastSpellOnPlayers(LIGHT_S_HAMMER_TELEPORT);
564 return;
565 }
566
567 me->setActive(true);
568 DoZoneInCombat();
569
570 events.SetPhase(PHASE_ONE);
571 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_SHAMBLING_HORROR, 20000, 0, PHASE_ONE);
572 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_DRUDGE_GHOUL, 10000, 0, PHASE_ONE);
573 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INFEST, 5000, 0, PHASE_ONE);
574 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_NECROTIC_PLAGUE, urand(30000, 33000), 0, PHASE_ONE);
575 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_BERSERK, 900000, EVENT_GROUP_BERSERK);
576 if (IsHeroic())
577 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHADOW_TRAP, 15500, 0, PHASE_ONE);
578 }
579
580 bool CanAIAttack(Unit const* target) const override
581 {
582 // The Lich King must not select targets in frostmourne room if he killed everyone outside
583 return !target->HasAura(SPELL_IN_FROSTMOURNE_ROOM) && BossAI::CanAIAttack(target);
584 }
585
586 void EnterEvadeMode(EvadeReason /*why*/) override
587 {
588 if (Creature* tirion = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING)))
589 tirion->DespawnOrUnsummon();
590 DoCastAOE(SPELL_KILL_FROSTMOURNE_PLAYERS);
591 EntryCheckPredicate pred(NPC_STRANGULATE_VEHICLE);
592 summons.DoAction(ACTION_TELEPORT_BACK, pred);
593 summons.DespawnAll();
594 _DespawnAtEvade();
595 }

599 if (victim->GetTypeId() == TYPEID_PLAYER && !me->IsInEvadeMode() && !events.IsInPhase(PHASE_OUTRO))
600 Talk(SAY_LK_KILL);

602
603 void DoAction(int32 action) override
604 {
605 switch (action)
606 {
607 case ACTION_START_ENCOUNTER:
608 instance->SetBossState(DATA_THE_LICH_KING, IN_PROGRESS);
609 Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_1);
610 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_FROZEN_THRONE);
611 // schedule talks
612 me->SetStandState(UNIT_STAND_STATE_STAND);
613 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INTRO_MOVE_1, 4000);
614 break;
615 case ACTION_START_ATTACK:
616 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_START_ATTACK, 5000);
617 break;
618 case ACTION_PLAY_MUSIC:
619 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_FINAL);
620 break;
621 case ACTION_RESTORE_LIGHT:
622 me->GetMap()->SetZoneOverrideLight(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, 0, 5000);
623 break;
624 case ACTION_BREAK_FROSTMOURNE:
625 me->CastSpell((Unit*)NULL, SPELL_SUMMON_BROKEN_FROSTMOURNE, TRIGGERED_IGNORE_CAST_IN_PROGRESS);
626 me->CastSpell((Unit*)NULL, SPELL_SUMMON_BROKEN_FROSTMOURNE_2, TRIGGERED_IGNORE_CAST_IN_PROGRESS);
627 SetEquipmentSlots(false, EQUIP_BROKEN_FROSTMOURNE);
628 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_6, 2500, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
629 break;
630 case ACTION_FINISH_OUTRO:
631 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_7, 7000, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
632 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_8, 17000, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
633 break;
634 case ACTION_TELEPORT_BACK:
635 {
636 EntryCheckPredicate pred(NPC_STRANGULATE_VEHICLE);
637 summons.DoAction(ACTION_TELEPORT_BACK, pred);
638 if (!IsHeroic())
639 Talk(SAY_LK_FROSTMOURNE_ESCAPE);
640 break;
641 }
642 default:
643 break;
644 }
645 }

677 void DamageTaken(Unit* /*attacker*/, uint32& /*damage*/) override
678 {
679 if (events.IsInPhase(PHASE_ONE) && !HealthAbovePct(70))
680 {
681 events.SetPhase(PHASE_TRANSITION);
682 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
683 me->AttackStop();
684 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_CENTER_1, CenterPosition);
685 return;

687
688 if (events.IsInPhase(PHASE_TWO) && !HealthAbovePct(40))

694 return;
695 }
696
697 if (events.IsInPhase(PHASE_THREE) && !HealthAbovePct(10))
698 {
699 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);

707 me->SetWalk(true);
708 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_1, 2600, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
709 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_EMOTE_TALK, 6600, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
710 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_EMOTE_TALK, 17600, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
711 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_EMOTE_TALK, 27600, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
712 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_2, 34600, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
713 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_3, 43600, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
714 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_EMOTE_CAST_SHOUT, 54600, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
715 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_EMOTE_TALK, 58600, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
716 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_MOVE_CENTER, 69600, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
717 // stop here. rest will get scheduled from MovementInform
718 return;

722 void JustSummoned(Creature* summon) override
723 {
724 switch (summon->GetEntry())
725 {
726 case NPC_SHAMBLING_HORROR:
727 case NPC_DRUDGE_GHOUL:
728 summon->CastSpell(summon, SPELL_RISEN_WITCH_DOCTOR_SPAWN, true);
729 summon->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
730 summon->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EMERGE);
731 summon->m_Events.AddEvent(new StartMovementEvent(me, summon), summon->m_Events.CalculateTime(5000));
732 break;
733 case NPC_ICE_SPHERE:
734 {
735 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 0, 0.0f, true))
736 {
737 summon->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
738 summon->CastSpell(summon, SPELL_ICE_SPHERE, false);
739 summon->CastSpell(summon, SPELL_ICE_BURST_TARGET_SEARCH, false);
740 summon->CastSpell(target, SPELL_ICE_PULSE, false);
741 summon->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING);
742 summon->GetMotionMaster()->MoveFollow(target, 0.0f, 0.0f);
743 }
744 else
745 summon->DespawnOrUnsummon();
746 break;
747 }
748 case NPC_DEFILE:
749 summon->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
750 summon->CastSpell(summon, SPELL_DEFILE_AURA, false);
751 break;
752 case NPC_FROSTMOURNE_TRIGGER:
753 {
754 summon->CastSpell((Unit*)NULL, SPELL_BROKEN_FROSTMOURNE, true);
755
756 me->GetMap()->SetZoneOverrideLight(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, LIGHT_SOULSTORM, 10000);
757 me->GetMap()->SetZoneWeather(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, WEATHER_STATE_BLACKSNOW, 0.5f);
758
759 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_SOUL_BARRAGE, 5000, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
760 return;
761 }
762 case NPC_VILE_SPIRIT:
763 {
764 summons.Summon(summon);
765 summon->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
766 summon->SetSpeed(MOVE_FLIGHT, 0.5f);
767 summon->GetMotionMaster()->MoveRandom(10.0f);
768 if (!events.IsInPhase(PHASE_FROSTMOURNE))
769 summon->m_Events.AddEvent(new VileSpiritActivateEvent(summon), summon->m_Events.CalculateTime(15000));
770 return;
771 }
772 case NPC_STRANGULATE_VEHICLE:
773 summons.Summon(summon);
774 return;
775 case NPC_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING_LK:
776 return;
777 default:
778 break;
779 }
780
781 BossAI::JustSummoned(summon);
782 }

816 void MovementInform(uint32 type, uint32 pointId) override
817 {
818 if (type != POINT_MOTION_TYPE)
819 return;

822 {
823 case POINT_LK_INTRO_1:

827 case POINT_LK_INTRO_2:

830 case POINT_LK_INTRO_3:

834 break;

838 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);

840 events.DelayEvents(62500, EVENT_GROUP_BERSERK); // delay berserk timer, its not ticking during phase transitions
841 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_QUAKE, 62500, 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
842 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING, 4000, 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
843 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE, 8000, 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
844 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_RAGING_SPIRIT, 3000, 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
845 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_VALKYR, 78000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
846 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INFEST, 70000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
847 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, 97000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
848 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER, 94000, 0, PHASE_TWO);
849 break;
850 case POINT_CENTER_2:
851 me->SetFacingTo(0.0f);
852 Talk(SAY_LK_REMORSELESS_WINTER);
853 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
854 DoCast(me, SPELL_REMORSELESS_WINTER_2);
855 summons.DespawnEntry(NPC_VALKYR_SHADOWGUARD);
856 events.DelayEvents(62500, EVENT_GROUP_BERSERK); // delay berserk timer, its not ticking during phase transitions
857 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_QUAKE_2, 62500, 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
858 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING, 6000, 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
859 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE, 8000, 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
860 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_RAGING_SPIRIT, 5000, 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
861 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, 95500, 0, PHASE_THREE);
862 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER, 99500, 0, PHASE_THREE);
863 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VILE_SPIRITS, 79500, EVENT_GROUP_VILE_SPIRITS, PHASE_THREE);
864 events.ScheduleEvent(IsHeroic() ? EVENT_HARVEST_SOULS : EVENT_HARVEST_SOUL, 73500, 0, PHASE_THREE);
865 break;
866 case POINT_LK_OUTRO_1:
867 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_4, 1, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
868 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_RAISE_DEAD, 1000, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);

870 break;
871 case POINT_LK_OUTRO_2:
872 if (Creature* tirion = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING)))
873 tirion->AI()->Talk(SAY_TIRION_OUTRO_2);
874 if (Creature* frostmourne = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_FROSTMOURNE_TRIGGER, 50.0f))
875 frostmourne->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_SUMMON_TERENAS);
876 break;
877 default:
878 break;

881
882 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
883 {
884 // check phase first to prevent updating victim and entering evade mode when not wanted
885 if (!(events.IsInPhase(PHASE_OUTRO) || events.IsInPhase(PHASE_INTRO) || events.IsInPhase(PHASE_FROSTMOURNE)))
886 if (!UpdateVictim())
887 return;
888
889 events.Update(diff);
890
891 // during Remorseless Winter phases The Lich King is channeling a spell, but we must continue casting other spells
892 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING) && !(events.IsInPhase(PHASE_TRANSITION) || events.IsInPhase(PHASE_OUTRO) || events.IsInPhase(PHASE_FROSTMOURNE)))
893 return;
894
895 while (uint32 eventId = events.ExecuteEvent())
896 {
897 switch (eventId)
898 {
899 case EVENT_INTRO_MOVE_1:
900 me->SetSheath(SHEATH_STATE_MELEE);
901 me->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_EMOTE_SIT_NO_SHEATH);
902 me->SetWalk(true);
903 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_LK_INTRO_1, LichKingIntro[0]);
904 break;
905 case EVENT_INTRO_MOVE_2:
906 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_LK_INTRO_2, LichKingIntro[1]);
907 break;
908 case EVENT_INTRO_MOVE_3:
909 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(POINT_LK_INTRO_3, LichKingIntro[2]);
910 break;
911 case EVENT_INTRO_TALK_1:
912 Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_2);
913 // for some reason blizz sends 2 emotes in row here so (we handle one in Talk)
914 me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_TALK_NO_SHEATHE);
915 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_EMOTE_CAST_SHOUT, 7000, 0, PHASE_INTRO);
916 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INTRO_EMOTE_1, 13000, 0, PHASE_INTRO);
917 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_EMOTE_CAST_SHOUT, 18000, 0, PHASE_INTRO);
918 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INTRO_CAST_FREEZE, 31000, 0, PHASE_INTRO);
919 break;
920 case EVENT_EMOTE_CAST_SHOUT:
921 DoCast(me, SPELL_EMOTE_SHOUT_NO_SHEATH, false);
922 break;
923 case EVENT_INTRO_EMOTE_1:
924 me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_POINT_NO_SHEATHE);
925 break;
926 case EVENT_INTRO_CAST_FREEZE:
927 Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_3);
928 DoCastAOE(SPELL_ICE_LOCK, false);
929 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_FINISH_INTRO, 1000, 0, PHASE_INTRO);
930 break;
931 case EVENT_FINISH_INTRO:
932 me->SetWalk(false);
933 me->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_IMMUNE_TO_PC);
934 me->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
935 events.SetPhase(PHASE_ONE);
936 break;
937 case EVENT_SUMMON_SHAMBLING_HORROR:
938 DoCast(me, SPELL_SUMMON_SHAMBLING_HORROR);
939 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
940 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_SHAMBLING_HORROR, 60000, 0, PHASE_ONE);
941 break;
942 case EVENT_SUMMON_DRUDGE_GHOUL:
943 DoCast(me, SPELL_SUMMON_DRUDGE_GHOULS);
944 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_DRUDGE_GHOUL, 30000, 0, PHASE_ONE);
945 break;
946 case EVENT_INFEST:
947 DoCast(me, SPELL_INFEST);
948 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INFEST, urand(21000, 24000), 0, events.IsInPhase(PHASE_ONE) ? PHASE_ONE : PHASE_TWO);
949 break;
950 case EVENT_NECROTIC_PLAGUE:
951 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 1, NecroticPlagueTargetCheck(me, NECROTIC_PLAGUE_LK, NECROTIC_PLAGUE_PLR)))
952 {
953 Talk(EMOTE_NECROTIC_PLAGUE_WARNING, target);
954 DoCast(target, SPELL_NECROTIC_PLAGUE);
955 }
956 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_NECROTIC_PLAGUE, urand(30000, 33000), 0, PHASE_ONE);
957 break;
958 case EVENT_SHADOW_TRAP:
959 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 0, NonTankTargetSelector(me)))
960 DoCast(target, SPELL_SHADOW_TRAP);
961 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHADOW_TRAP, 15500, 0, PHASE_ONE);
962 break;
963 case EVENT_SOUL_REAPER:
964 DoCastVictim(SPELL_SOUL_REAPER);
965 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER, urand(33000, 35000), 0, PHASE_TWO_THREE);
966 break;
967 case EVENT_DEFILE:
968 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 1, 0.0f, true, -SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL_VALKYR))
969 {
970 Talk(EMOTE_DEFILE_WARNING);
971 DoCast(target, SPELL_DEFILE);
972 }
973 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, urand(32000, 35000), 0, PHASE_TWO_THREE);
974 break;
975 case EVENT_HARVEST_SOUL:
976 Talk(SAY_LK_HARVEST_SOUL);
977 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 0, SpellTargetSelector(me, SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL)))
978 DoCast(target, SPELL_HARVEST_SOUL);
979 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_HARVEST_SOUL, 75000, 0, PHASE_THREE);
980 break;
981 case EVENT_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING:
982 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 0, 0.0f, true))
983 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING, TRIGGERED_NONE);
984 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PAIN_AND_SUFFERING, urand(1500, 4000), 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
985 break;
986 case EVENT_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE:
987 DoCastAOE(SPELL_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE);
988 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_ICE_SPHERE, urand(7500, 8500), 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
989 break;
990 case EVENT_SUMMON_RAGING_SPIRIT:
991 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 0, 0.0f, true))
992 me->CastSpell(target, SPELL_RAGING_SPIRIT, TRIGGERED_NONE);
993 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_RAGING_SPIRIT, urand(22000, 23000), 0, PHASE_TRANSITION);
994 break;
995 case EVENT_QUAKE:
996 events.SetPhase(PHASE_TWO);
997 me->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING); // clear state to ensure check in DoCastAOE passes
998 DoCastAOE(SPELL_QUAKE);
999 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
1000 Talk(SAY_LK_QUAKE);
1001 break;
1002 case EVENT_QUAKE_2:
1003 events.SetPhase(PHASE_THREE);
1004 me->ClearUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING); // clear state to ensure check in DoCastAOE passes
1005 DoCastAOE(SPELL_QUAKE);
1006 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
1007 Talk(SAY_LK_QUAKE);
1008 break;
1009 case EVENT_SUMMON_VALKYR:
1010 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
1011 Talk(SAY_LK_SUMMON_VALKYR);
1012 DoCastAOE(SUMMON_VALKYR);
1013 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_VALKYR, urand(45000, 50000), 0, PHASE_TWO);
1014 break;
1015 case EVENT_START_ATTACK:
1016 me->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
1017 if (events.IsInPhase(PHASE_FROSTMOURNE))
1018 events.SetPhase(PHASE_THREE);
1019 break;
1020 case EVENT_VILE_SPIRITS:
1021 me->GetMap()->SetZoneMusic(AREA_THE_FROZEN_THRONE, MUSIC_SPECIAL);
1022 DoCastAOE(SPELL_VILE_SPIRITS);
1023 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VILE_SPIRITS, urand(35000, 40000), EVENT_GROUP_VILE_SPIRITS, PHASE_THREE);
1024 break;
1025 case EVENT_HARVEST_SOULS:
1026 Talk(SAY_LK_HARVEST_SOUL);
1027 DoCastAOE(SPELL_HARVEST_SOULS);
1028 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_HARVEST_SOULS, urand(100000, 110000), 0, PHASE_THREE);
1029 events.SetPhase(PHASE_FROSTMOURNE); // will stop running UpdateVictim (no evading)
1030 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
1031 me->AttackStop();
1032 events.DelayEvents(50000, EVENT_GROUP_VILE_SPIRITS);
1033 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_DEFILE, 50000, 0, PHASE_THREE);
1034 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_SOUL_REAPER, urand(57000, 62000), 0, PHASE_THREE);
1035 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_START_ATTACK, 49000);
1036 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_FROSTMOURNE_HEROIC, 6500);
1037 break;
1038 case EVENT_FROSTMOURNE_HEROIC:
1039 if (TempSummon* terenas = me->GetMap()->SummonCreature(NPC_TERENAS_MENETHIL_FROSTMOURNE_H, TerenasSpawnHeroic, NULL, 50000))
1040 {
1041 terenas->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_FROSTMOURNE_INTRO);
1042 std::list<Creature*> triggers;
1043 GetCreatureListWithEntryInGrid(triggers, terenas, NPC_WORLD_TRIGGER_INFINITE_AOI, 100.0f);
1044 if (!triggers.empty())
1045 {
1046 triggers.sort(Trinity::ObjectDistanceOrderPred(terenas, true));
1047 Creature* spawner = triggers.front();
1048 spawner->CastSpell(spawner, SPELL_SUMMON_SPIRIT_BOMB_1, true); // summons bombs randomly
1049 spawner->CastSpell(spawner, SPELL_SUMMON_SPIRIT_BOMB_2, true); // summons bombs on players
1050 spawner->m_Events.AddEvent(new TriggerWickedSpirit(spawner), spawner->m_Events.CalculateTime(3000));
1051 }
1052
1053 for (SummonList::iterator i = summons.begin(); i != summons.end(); ++i)
1054 {
1055 Creature* summon = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, *i);
1056 if (summon && summon->GetEntry() == NPC_VILE_SPIRIT)
1057 {
1058 summon->m_Events.KillAllEvents(true);
1059 summon->m_Events.AddEvent(new VileSpiritActivateEvent(summon), summon->m_Events.CalculateTime(50000));
1060 summon->GetMotionMaster()->MoveRandom(10.0f);
1061 summon->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
1062 }
1063 }
1064 }
1065 break;
1066 case EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_1:
1067 Talk(SAY_LK_OUTRO_1);
1068 DoCastAOE(SPELL_FURY_OF_FROSTMOURNE_NO_REZ, true);
1069 break;
1070 case EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_2:
1071 Talk(SAY_LK_OUTRO_2);
1072 DoCastAOE(SPELL_EMOTE_QUESTION_NO_SHEATH);
1073 break;
1074 case EVENT_OUTRO_EMOTE_TALK:
1075 me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_TALK_NO_SHEATHE);
1076 break;
1077 case EVENT_OUTRO_TALK_3:
1078 if (Creature* tirion = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING)))
1079 me->SetFacingToObject(tirion);

1744 if (damage >= me->GetHealth())
1745 {
1746 damage = me->GetHealth() - 1;
1747 if (!me->HasAura(SPELL_TERENAS_LOSES_INSIDE) && !IsHeroic())
1748 {
1749 me->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
1750 DoCast(SPELL_TERENAS_LOSES_INSIDE);
1751 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TELEPORT_BACK, 1000);
1752 if (Creature* warden = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_SPIRIT_WARDEN, 20.0f))
1753 {
1754 warden->CastSpell((Unit*)NULL, SPELL_DESTROY_SOUL, TRIGGERED_NONE);
1755 warden->DespawnOrUnsummon(2000);
1756 }
1757
1758 me->DespawnOrUnsummon(2000);
1759 }
1760 }
1761 }
1762
1763 void IsSummonedBy(Unit* /*summoner*/) override
1764 {
1765 _events.Reset();
1766 _events.SetPhase(PHASE_OUTRO);
1767 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
1768 me->SetFacingToObject(lichKing);
1769
1770 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_TERENAS_TALK_1, 2000, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
1771 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTRO_TERENAS_TALK_2, 14000, 0, PHASE_OUTRO);
1772 }
1773
1774 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
1775 {
1776 UpdateVictim();
1777
1778 _events.Update(diff);
1779
1780 while (uint32 eventId = _events.ExecuteEvent())
1781 {
1782 switch (eventId)
1783 {
1784 case EVENT_FROSTMOURNE_TALK_1:
1785 Talk(SAY_TERENAS_INTRO_1);
1786 if (IsHeroic())
1787 DoCastAOE(SPELL_RESTORE_SOULS);
1788 break;
1789 case EVENT_FROSTMOURNE_TALK_2:
1790 Talk(SAY_TERENAS_INTRO_2);
1791 break;
1792 case EVENT_FROSTMOURNE_TALK_3:
1793 Talk(SAY_TERENAS_INTRO_3);
1794 break;
1795 case EVENT_OUTRO_TERENAS_TALK_1:
1796 Talk(SAY_TERENAS_OUTRO_1);
1797 break;
1798 case EVENT_OUTRO_TERENAS_TALK_2:
1799 Talk(SAY_TERENAS_OUTRO_2);
1800 DoCastAOE(SPELL_MASS_RESURRECTION);
1801 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
1802 {
1803 lichKing->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_FINISH_OUTRO);
1804 lichKing->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_IMMUNE_TO_NPC);
1805 if (Creature* tirion = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_HIGHLORD_TIRION_FORDRING)))
1806 tirion->AI()->AttackStart(lichKing);
1807 }
1808 break;
1809 case EVENT_DESTROY_SOUL:
1810 me->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
1811 if (Creature* warden = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_SPIRIT_WARDEN, 20.0f))
1812 warden->CastSpell((Unit*)NULL, SPELL_DESTROY_SOUL, TRIGGERED_NONE);
1813 DoCast(SPELL_TERENAS_LOSES_INSIDE);
1814 _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TELEPORT_BACK, 1000);
1815 break;
1816 case EVENT_TELEPORT_BACK:
1817 if (Creature* lichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _instance->GetGuidData(DATA_THE_LICH_KING)))
1818 lichKing->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_TELEPORT_BACK);
1819 break;
1820 default:
1821 break;
1822 }
1823 }
1824
1825 // fighting Spirit Warden
1826 if (me->IsInCombat())
1827 DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
1828 }
1829
1830 private:
1831 EventMap _events;
1832 InstanceScript* _instance;
1833 };

1836 {

1838 }
